'''脂肪肉瘤（{{lang-en|Liposarcoma}}）'''，是一种由[[脂肪细胞|脂肪细胞]]在深层[[软组织|软组织]]（如[[腹膜|腹膜]]后或大腿内侧）异常增生导致的[[癌症|癌症]]。<ref name="pmid10982304">{{cite journal |author=Dei Tos AP |title=Liposarcoma: new entities and evolving concepts |journal=Ann Diagn Pathol |volume=4 |issue=4 |pages=252–66 |date=August 2000 |pmid=10982304 |doi=10.1053/adpa.2000.8133 |url=http://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S1092-9134(00)74153-0 |access-date=2016-04-29 |archive-date=2018-09-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180901113134/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S1092-9134(00)74153-0 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 脂肪肉瘤是一种罕见的恶性肿瘤，显微观察显示其与普通脂肪细胞类似。<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://sarcomahelp.org/liposarcoma.html|title = What is Liposarcoma?|date = October 2012|accessdate = 2015-04-22|website = The Liddy Shriver Sarcoma Initiative|publisher = |last = Bell|first = Teresa|archive-date = 2018-07-09|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180709165121/http://sarcomahelp.org/liposarcoma.html|dead-url = yes}}</ref>

脂肪肉瘤通常为巨大的肿瘤，并且在最大的肿瘤周围常伴有数个体积较小的肿瘤。

脂肪肉瘤与其他[[肉瘤|肉瘤]]一样，十分罕见。<ref name="centers">{{cite web|author=Goldstein-Rice, E|year=2008|title=The Importance of Treatment at a Specialty Center for Sarcomas|work=ESUN|url=http://sarcomahelp.org/sarcoma-centers.html|accessdate=2016-04-29|archive-date=2017-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171210013020/http://sarcomahelp.org/sarcoma-centers.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==症状与体征==
[[Image:edemaliposarcoma.jpg|thumb]]
症状通常为患者报告有异物生长在软组织内，并且会导致疼痛或影响日常生活。

生长在腹膜后的脂肪肉瘤会导致体重减轻、消瘦和[[腹痛|腹痛]]，并且可能由于压迫[[肾脏|肾脏]]与[[输尿管|输尿管]]而导致[[肾衰竭|肾衰竭]]。

==诊断==
[[Image:Liposarcoma_02.jpg|thumb]]
公认的诊断方法为进行[[组织学|组织学]]检查，即切除并[[活检|活检]]。活检通常会观察到成脂细胞，一种充满多个[[胞浆|胞浆]]空泡，并且有由空泡导致的染色剂无法上色产生的黑色核的脂肪细胞。

===亚型===
脂肪肉瘤有多种亚型:
* 高分化脂肪肉瘤（Well-differentiated liposarcoma）, synonymous with atypical lipomatous tumor—the former term is used almost exclusively for lesions in the [[retroperitoneum|retroperitoneum]], while the latter is used for lesions arising elsewhere
* 去分化型脂肪肉瘤—高分化型脂肪肉瘤（Dedifferentiated liposarcoma—well-differentiated liposarcoma） adjacent to a more poorly differentiated tumor
* 圆形细胞型脂肪肉瘤（粘液细胞型脂肪肉瘤）（myxoid cell liposarcoma）
* 多形型脂肪肉瘤（Pleomorphic liposarcoma）

